Record Offset has index: i32; value: i32.

To write offset offset: Offset into cells: buffer of 4 i32.
cells at offset.index becomes offset.value.

To main, giving i32.
Let cells be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0.
Let offset be Offset with index be 2 and value be 9.
Write offset offset into cells.
Give cells at 2.
